    <div id="tocRoot"></div>
    
    <p class="module-desc"><p>Experimental support for direct left recursion in NPeg</p>
<p>This module implements direct left-recursion detection and handling based on the algorithm described in &quot;Left Recursion in Parsing Expression Grammars&quot; by Sergio Medeiros et al.</p>
<p>Basic usage:</p>
<p><pre class="listing"><span class="Keyword">import</span> <span class="Identifier">npeg</span>
<span class="Keyword">import</span> <span class="Identifier">npeg</span><span class="Operator">/</span><span class="Identifier">leftrec</span>  <span class="Comment"># Required for left recursion support</span>

<span class="Comment"># Define a left-recursive grammar</span>
<span class="Keyword">let</span> <span class="Identifier">parser</span> <span class="Operator">=</span> <span class="Identifier">peg</span> <span class="StringLit">&quot;expr&quot;</span><span class="Punctuation">:</span>
  <span class="Identifier">expr</span> <span class="Operator">&lt;-</span> <span class="Identifier">expr</span> <span class="Operator">*</span> <span class="StringLit">&quot;+&quot;</span> <span class="Operator">*</span> <span class="Identifier">term</span> <span class="Operator">|</span> <span class="Identifier">term</span>
  <span class="Identifier">term</span> <span class="Operator">&lt;-</span> <span class="Operator">+</span><span class="Identifier">Digit</span>

<span class="Comment"># Parse left-recursive expressions</span>
<span class="Identifier">assert</span> <span class="Identifier">parser</span><span class="Operator">.</span><span class="Identifier">match</span><span class="Punctuation">(</span><span class="StringLit">&quot;1+2+3&quot;</span><span class="Punctuation">)</span><span class="Operator">.</span><span class="Identifier">ok</span></pre></p>
<p>Features:</p>
<ul class="simple"><li>Automatic detection and handling of direct left recursion</li>
<li>Transparent integration with NPeg grammar syntax</li>
<li>Based on proven algorithms from PEG research</li>
<li>Supports complex expression parsing patterns</li>
</ul>
<p>Limitations:</p>
<ul class="simple"><li>Currently supports only direct left recursion</li>
<li>Indirect/mutual left recursion has limited support</li>
<li>May impact parsing performance for left-recursive grammars</li>
</ul>
<p>Note: This is an experimental feature and API might change in the future.</p>
</p>
